{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9e572c33bf","title":"张一樵谈“遵义事件” （记录稿）","origin":"张再兴编《1959-1960年“贵州事件”资料集》（贵阳，2002）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"20f0072339","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":29,"articleId":"9e572c33bf"}],"tags":[{"id":"4f45e132a9","name":"贵州文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"133ade5f34","name":"贵州"},{"id":"1e6ff25b59","name":"张一樵"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dee179d149","type":"title","text":"张一樵谈“遵义事件” （记录稿）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"03174ab6c5","type":"authors","text":"贵州张一樵","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"fe2e2a655f","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1967年6月29日","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"00a6e3efad","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：贵州工学院学生宿舍5902-325室","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"b75c9f9f0f","type":"paragraph","text":"采访人：矿业学院东方红、人民大学三红等3人，贵州工学院“九·一五”等数人","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"c3e122381e","type":"paragraph","text":"被采访人：张一樵(时任贵阳市长)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"1dec15e3ce","type":"paragraph","text":"张：65年11月，邓小平、薄一波、李富春、李井泉来了。21号或22号上午，在金桥饭店接见我们，我们去了。贾启允汇报了三线建设情况及农业生产情况。李井泉讲厂社结合问题。叫办厂的向社员讲，社员的儿子将来可以参加工厂，这样，农民就爱厂了，吃菜也有了。20%作内换工。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"e2a58d93e1","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平讲建党建团问题。讲过去没发展，不要急，通过四清后发展。说到“四清”问题，要组成“四清”专业队。他介绍说，中南有20万，华东18万，还讲贵州也可以搞他2万、2万5。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"bb4e94bb66","type":"paragraph","text":"还谈到“过去的‘四清’一风吹，今后来过”。这实际上就是把周林的案翻了，“一风吹了”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"e5ab18f973","type":"paragraph","text":"65年7月贾他个人从西南局回来，拿了一件决议文件，原处理周林的文件是说他犯右倾机会主义路线性质的错误，而他拿来的文件中把“路线”二字去掉了。他还说，周的问题和邓子恢、曾希圣的性质不同，说周林未公开提出单干。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"},{"id":"ecf2e8fd1d","type":"paragraph","text":"结束。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf"}],"page":{"id":"4fa5d6a39e","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9e572c33bf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}